author: Special Correspondent
title: One virus death in Rajasthan
description: 13 new cases, including two who attended Tabligh meet
content: An 85-year-old man from Alwar, who had tested COVID-19 positive and was admitted to Sawai Man Singh Government Hospital here two days ago, died on Thursday. Thirteen more cases of patients infected with COVID-19, including three who attended a Tablighi Jamaat… [+1332 chars]
